Trade/Device Name(s): OneTouch UltraMini Blood Glucose Monitoring System
OneTouch Lancing Device with AST Clear Cap
OneTouch UltraSoft Blood Sampler with OneTouch UltraClear Cap
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for OneTouch UltraMini Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary whole blood.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood, for in vitro diagnostic use by people with diabetes at home and healthcare professionals in clinical settings; specifically indicated for use on the finger, forearm, or palm.
